+    // Two tests cover this, both of which must fail if the ordering regresses
+    // to add_bias_gelu-then-adapter (delta landing after GELU instead of
+    // before):
+    //   - `test_ffn_intermediate_stage_lora_delta_lands_before_gelu` runs by
